EXTRACTED VALUE: I was rather disappointed with the single player game. I was able to finish all of the single player missions with just a few hours of gameplay.
The game can be a little restrictive but the campaign mode is enjoyable and is sure to satisfy World War II FPS fans.
Fans of the character and the action sequences will likely find plenty to enjoy, but anyone expecting something more will be disappointed.
It’s not particularly innovative, it doesn’t have ground breaking graphics, but it does what it’s meant to do and is a fun way to spend a little time.
